{
  "texts": [
    "SFT/RL Ratio.",
    "We have about 5k prompts in SFT and about 14k prompts in RL stage.",
    "Rubric Verifier Evaluation.",
    "To evaluate how well the rubric verifier aligns with human judgment, we collect a holdout validation set of our rubric verifier training data in Section 4.3, which has human labels about whether each response satisfies each rubric of a prompt.",
    "We then compare the agreement between the human labels and the labels predicted by both the finetuned rubric verifier and the vanilla prompted LLM judge (Llama 4 Maverick), which share the same prompt template as in Section 3.1."
  ]
}